pageProduct.name: Swisse Ultiboost Co Enzyme Q10 150mg 180 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Swisse Ultiboost Co-Enzyme Q10 is a premium quality, one-a-day formula to help maintain cardiovascular system health and reduce free radical damage to body cells.

Heart Health: Co-enzyme Q10 supports heart health and a healthy cardiovascular system.

Antioxidant Support: Co-enzyme Q10 provides antioxidant support and helps reduce free radical damage to body cells.   
Energy Production: Co-enzyme Q10 is present in most cells of the body and supports energy production.

Aging Support: There may be an increased need for supplemental co-enzyme Q10 in the elderly due to levels decreasing with age.

Size: 180 Capsules

Warnings

Do not take while on warfarin therapy without medical advice.

Ingredients

EACH CAPSULE CONTAINS:
CO-ENZYME Q10 (ubidecarenone) 150 mg
Contains phenylalanine, soya beans & sulfites.
No added lactose, gluten, yeast, egg, artificial colours or flavours.

Directions

DIRECTIONS FOR USE - ADULT DOSAGE:
One capsule daily, during or immediately after a meal, or as directed by a healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C in a cool, dry place.
